cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as summarization is a common task in IR. Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the focus on multi-document summarization could also place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
